then the gauge field equations of motion are satisfied trivially
for the constant gauge field strength . Then the
problem reduces to the situation where we have to solve only the
tachyon equation of motion under the background of the field
strength which appears only in the open string metric. In our
case the explicit form of the inverse open string metric is
 
where .  The metric in the
